latestPosts.caption:
Would you try this exciting Colour Analysis session?👇🏻🤩

I kept seeing all those viral Colour Analysis reels and was so curious to try it for myself and trust me, I had the most eye-opening session with the amazing @stylistsejalagarwal @thestyleplanner.co 🙌🏻

My experience? 100/10! I got to know everything right from the colours that suit me best, to metals, makeup, hair colour, jewellery, gemstones, lenses, how to create outfit combinations… everything!!!

One of my absolute favourite takeaways? Realising I’m a gold-tone person rather than silver. 🤯 Seeing my personal palette laid out was such a MIND-BLOWING moment.🌈

📍She’s based in India and does pre-booked sessions in Dubai (she usually announces dates on Instagram). In-person sessions happen throughout the year in Pune, India and the best part is, you can even get it done online! 💻✨

Honestly, the session was so informative and practical I can actually apply it in real life. Being a fashion lover myself, I truly enjoyed every bit of it. It was such an eye-opener!

If you’ve been wanting to discover the colours that actually flatter you based on your personality and natural features, I HIGHLY recommend this session. 💯✨
